OL,6,FWeekend working is unpopular with most
OL,7,Fdrivers, the tribunal heard, with
OL,8,Fstaff required to work slightly longer
OL,9,Fshifts than in the week.
OL,11,FDrivers at the Hainault depot are
OL,12,Fusually required to work approximately
OL,13,F50% of weekends, the tribunal was told.
