OL,3,CMaking female train driver work
OL,4,CSaturdays 'is not sex discrimination'
OL,6,FIn November 2020, Ms Jones was invited
OL,7,Fto a meeting with her manager at which
OL,8,Fshe was told her usual flexible
OL,9,Fworking arrangement was coming to an
OL,10,Fend due to the "detrimental impact ...
OL,11,Fto the quality of service London
OL,12,FUnderground was able to provide its
OL,13,Fcustomers".
OL,15,FBetween May 24 and June 13 2021, Ms
OL,16,FJones was off work because of the
OL,17,Feffects of her reaction to a Covid
OL,18,Fvaccine.
