OL,6,FAfter returning from sick leave, she
OL,7,Fwas unable to do her usual work, and
OL,8,Fwas given alternative duties at
OL,9,FLiverpool Street station, where it was
OL,10,Fnot possible for her to work the same
OL,11,Fshift patterns she had at Hainault,
OL,12,Fthe tribunal was told.
OL,14,FRejecting Ms Jones' claims of direct
OL,15,Fsex discrimination and indirect sex
OL,16,Fdiscrimination, employment Judge
OL,17,FStephen Shore said there was "no
OL,18,Fevidence" to show a "hypothetical
OL,19,Fmale" would have been treated
OL,20,Fdifferently.
